think how it would be if more people learn about it and all the different type games that are coming out b/c there will be more people addicted (not everyone mind you).  I know this is a totally random thought and may not happen, but thought I would share. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <p>&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Revnick Lifeweaver&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;2&quot;&gt; <br>
